        "subject": "LU-2779 osc: to not wait extent with interrupt enabled",
        "message": "LU-2779 osc: to not wait extent with interrupt enabled\n\nThis will cause assert at discard_cb() as follows:\n\nASSERTION( (!(page->cp_type == CPT_CACHEABLE) ||\n\t(!PageWriteback(cl_page_vmpage(env, page)))) ) failed:\n(cl_lock.c:1964:discard_cb()) LBUG\nCall Trace:\n libcfs_debug_dumpstack+0x55/0x80 [libcfs]\n lbug_with_loc+0x47/0xb0 [libcfs]\n discard_cb+0x1c4/0x1d0 [obdclass]\n cl_page_gang_lookup+0x1d4/0x3d0 [obdclass]\n cl_lock_discard_pages+0x11e/0x1f0 [obdclass]\n osc_lock_flush+0xff/0x280 [osc]\n osc_lock_cancel+0xe7/0x1c0 [osc]\n cl_lock_cancel0+0x75/0x160 [obdclass]\n cl_lock_cancel+0x13b/0x140 [obdclass]\n osc_ldlm_blocking_ast+0x13a/0x350 [osc]\n ldlm_cancel_callback+0x6c/0x1a0 [ptlrpc]\n ldlm_cli_cancel_local+0x8a/0x470 [ptlrpc]\n ldlm_cli_cancel_list_local+0xee/0x290 [ptlrpc]\n ldlm_cancel_lru_local+0x35/0x40 [ptlrpc]\n ldlm_prep_elc_req+0x3ec/0x4b0 [ptlrpc]\n ldlm_prep_enqueue_req+0x28/0x30 [ptlrpc]\n osc_enqueue_base+0x113/0x590 [osc]\n ...\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie9ed5fb3bc1479d4f5f37b5cda384ba3c0e77518\n"
